pd_0_com_0text: Captain! Thank you for saving us!
pd_1_com_1text: Happy to see you guys all in one piece.
pd_2_com_0text: We are injured and we cannot fight, but we can manage to get out of here alone. Careful captain, we are near the Master's hall...
pd_3_com_0text: The Master will pay for his crimes.
pd_4_com_0text: Listen captain, before you go, there is one thing we'd like to ask... If you manage to kill the Master...  What should we do right after?
pd_5_com_0text: We should go back to our castle and build our defences.
pd_5_com_1text: We should find the lasty troops of the Master and kill them without mercy.
pd_5_com_2text: We should call our allies in the nearby kingdoms. United we stand, divided we fall.
pd_6_com_0text: Wise words from our captain! Thank you... for everything.
